  "logNo": "223500018660",
  "title": "많이 아픈 회전근개 석회, 어깨에 석회가 생겼데요~",
  "addDate": "2024. 7. 3.",
  "categoryNo": "21",
  "parentCategoryNo": "7",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=223500018660",
  "html_size": 224217,
  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87b382b4-1e54-11f0-8dab-55105e43ff75\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3828e-1e54-11f0-8dab-b9dd751667e8\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3828d-1e54-11f0-8dab-591d907d8a06\">어깨가 아픈 중년의 환자분들 중에 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b38290-1e54-11f0-8dab-e5095c5118ba\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3828f-1e54-11f0-8dab-fd87f0df2ef7\">‘사진 찍어보니 어깨에 석회가 있다고 해요’</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b38292-1e54-11f0-8dab-395df9ed1f66\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b38291-1e54-11f0-8dab-8b49aeb0371c\">라고 호소하시는 분들이 종종 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b38294-1e54-11f0-8dab-715626188eca\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b38293-1e54-11f0-8dab-17fd4c2a8a5c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b38296-1e54-11f0-8dab-35a68ab6d93b\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b38295-1e54-11f0-8dab-9392bf4720ae\">혹은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b38298-1e54-11f0-8dab-11733a680c65\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b38297-1e54-11f0-8dab-538f1e436c0b\">어깨가 아프다고 왔는데, 이수한의원에서 초음파로 어깨 관절을 확인하다가 석회가 발견되는 경우도 적지 않아요</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3829a-1e54-11f0-8dab-cba85fa94b6c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b38299-1e54-11f0-8dab-5573d78945eb\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3829c-1e54-11f0-8dab-0b53bc12f202\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3829b-1e54-11f0-8dab-6d0ac0753bb3\">‘석회가 왜 생겨요?’</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3829e-1e54-11f0-8dab-571d8482cbc4\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3829d-1e54-11f0-8dab-3b55ffffcfb1\">‘석회 생긴거, 어떻게 해야해요?’</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b382a0-1e54-11f0-8dab-4d0e05541cc8\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3829f-1e54-11f0-8dab-a15a563bd7ec\">‘팔을 많이 쓰지도 않는데 이런게 생길 수가 있나요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b382a2-1e54-11f0-8dab-63d261bcf66d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b382a1-1e54-11f0-8dab-bfc729f8eb1a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b382a4-1e54-11f0-8dab-95078f602489\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b382a3-1e54-11f0-8dab-c3a556974deb\">환자분들의 궁금증은 끝이 없죠 ^^ </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b382a6-1e54-11f0-8dab-b134b029fd1a\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b382a5-1e54-11f0-8dab-d10b90e30848\">당연히 궁금하시겠죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b382a8-1e54-11f0-8dab-b5128400b8d6\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b382a7-1e54-11f0-8dab-7d5882cc3048\">당장 어깨가 너무 아픈데, 어깨에 석회가 꼈다고 하니 걱정도 되고 빨리 어떻게든 치료하고 싶으실 겁니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b382aa-1e54-11f0-8dab-9fc772418a02\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b382a9-1e54-11f0-8dab-81777e067e1d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b382ac-1e54-11f0-8dab-11a69bda7101\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b382ab-1e54-11f0-8dab-2b9d07a41944\">그래서 오늘 어깨(회전근개-Rotator cuff)의 석회화(calcification)에 대해 포스팅해볼께요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b382ae-1e54-11f0-8dab-5ba9f7d431c3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b382ad-1e54-11f0-8dab-8f44a039d51e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b382b0-1e54-11f0-8dab-d519fb06ee08\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b382af-1e54-11f0-8dab-a7fdda5405f3\">2018년에 발표된 리뷰 논문에 관련 내용이 잘 정리되어 있어서 그 논문의 내용중 피료한 부분만 정리해서 알려드리도록 하겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b382b2-1e54-11f0-8dab-b1bba11e97f0\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b382b1-1e54-11f0-8dab-4d87603fd8d0\"><a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6179075/\" class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"text\" data-linkdata='{\"id\": \"SE-87b382b1-1e54-11f0-8dab-4d87603fd8d0\", \"link\": \"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6179075/\"}' target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6179075/</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-87b382b4-1e54-11f0-8dab-55105e43ff75\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87b382b5-1e54-11f0-8dab-77dddd53ef2b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-right\" style=\"max-width:375px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-87b382b5-1e54-11f0-8dab-77dddd53ef2b\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0aa93f777abfad4d.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2179\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1710\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0aa93f777abfad4d.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0aa93f777abfad4d.jpg\" data-width=\"375\" data-height=\"294\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-87b382b5-1e54-11f0-8dab-77dddd53ef2b\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87b382bd-1e54-11f0-8dab-2bdda173a47e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b382b7-1e54-11f0-8dab-73766685915c\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b382b6-1e54-11f0-8dab-fdd9a1389164\">회전근개(어깨를 잡아주는 주요 힘줄 4가지를 말한다)의 석회와 건병증(또는 석회성 건염, 석회성 힘줄염) 은 건강한 성인 100명 중 2.5명~ 7.5명(연구마다 발표하는 숫자가 달라요)에게서 발병합니다. 그 중 70%는 여성이고, 특히 40-50대 여성에게 호발합니다. 신체활동(노동 및 운동 등)과는 상관이 없어 보인다고 합니다. 대부분은 오른쪽 또는 왼쪽, 한쪽에만 발병하는데, 10-20% 정도에서는 양쪽이 같이 발병하기도 한답니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b382b9-1e54-11f0-8dab-6313e4d748b5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b382b8-1e54-11f0-8dab-1dcb41ed38d5\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b382bb-1e54-11f0-8dab-1fa57b323953\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b382ba-1e54-11f0-8dab-e9be6e4eaac6\">&quot;견우혈&quot;에 해당하는 극상근의 힘줄에 발병하는 비율이 80%나 되니, 거의 다 극상근 힘줄에 석회가 발생한다고 보면 되겠고, 15%는 극하근, 5%는 견갑하근에 발생한다 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-195ad2bc-4962-48e9-a6ee-8e0947a13251\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-5f1fa117-1ea6-443a-a951-76923c072c48\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-87b382bd-1e54-11f0-8dab-2bdda173a47e\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87b382be-1e54-11f0-8dab-1532160039d8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-right\" style=\"max-width:375px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-87b382be-1e54-11f0-8dab-1532160039d8\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fc12939914a28d9d.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2606\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1449\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fc12939914a28d9d.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fc12939914a28d9d.jpg\" data-width=\"375\" data-height=\"208\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b382c0-1e54-11f0-8dab-532573068e00\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b382bf-1e54-11f0-8dab-6db017fef4b9\">극상근 힘줄에 생긴 석회의 이미지</span></p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-87b382be-1e54-11f0-8dab-1532160039d8\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87b3a9f6-1e54-11f0-8dab-4be3fcc4a426\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9d2-1e54-11f0-8dab-13667adc205f\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9d1-1e54-11f0-8dab-e77544aab2ba\">어깨 이외의 신체부위로는 고관절을 외회전하는 힘줄에 잘 생기는데, &quot;환도혈&quot;에 해당하는 고관절의 뒤쪽 부위가 되겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9d4-1e54-11f0-8dab-99f15a8cae22\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9d3-1e54-11f0-8dab-b7cc3e4db805\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9d6-1e54-11f0-8dab-810fb5817525\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9d5-1e54-11f0-8dab-6be2aa9a79c4\">석회성 힘줄염의 20% 정도는 통증이 없거나 경미하며, 약간의 움직임 제한이 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9d8-1e54-11f0-8dab-9f63eb2da2c7\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9d7-1e54-11f0-8dab-6dba4f5d75ce\">석회는 자연적으로 흡수되어 사라질 수도 있는데, 석회 침착은 힘줄의 퇴행성 변화와는 상관이 없는 것으로 보입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9da-1e54-11f0-8dab-2b9ee6207b62\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9d9-1e54-11f0-8dab-416604e33b4b\">어떤 경우에는 극심한 통증을 호소하고, 밤에 더 통증이 심해집니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9dc-1e54-11f0-8dab-c37e5e871112\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9db-1e54-11f0-8dab-adeb521ecc04\">대다수 증상(통증 및 움직임 제한)이 있는 석회성 힘줄염은 휴식, 소염진통제(NSIADs), 스테로이드 주사, 물리치료(혹 도수, 추나 치료) 에 반응하여 호전을 보입니다.  </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9de-1e54-11f0-8dab-fb0b2b324939\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9dd-1e54-11f0-8dab-f9232888e871\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9e0-1e54-11f0-8dab-e1c58c72ca84\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9df-1e54-11f0-8dab-41d249e92005\">(이수한의원에서는 물리치료, 침치료, 약침치료, 한약치료, 추나치료 등을 어깨의 상태에 맞게 적절하게 선택하여 치료하고 있습니다) </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9e2-1e54-11f0-8dab-9725b7a45d07\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9e1-1e54-11f0-8dab-5f12d9657f43\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9e4-1e54-11f0-8dab-41594af6e234\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9e3-1e54-11f0-8dab-418428008021\">석회성 힘줄염에 대한 표준화된 치료법은 없고 여러 보존적 치료방법들과 수술, 충격파 등이 필요할 수도 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9e6-1e54-11f0-8dab-c90fdbe4d4f7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9e5-1e54-11f0-8dab-09b9616bc312\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9e8-1e54-11f0-8dab-27e25ea6f297\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9e7-1e54-11f0-8dab-6f336a4e84e3\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9ea-1e54-11f0-8dab-4ff9f14073b5\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9e9-1e54-11f0-8dab-d9290788dc68\">왜 석회성 힘줄염이 생기는지는 아직도 모릅니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9ec-1e54-11f0-8dab-3ba9ed8611a8\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9eb-1e54-11f0-8dab-453dd4c5ae41\">몇 가지 가설이 있지만, 아직 완전히 밝혀지지 않았어요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9ee-1e54-11f0-8dab-a7f7b19cdaff\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9ed-1e54-11f0-8dab-bb7be326ded3\">석회는 생겼다가 재흡수 되면서 다시 힘줄이 회복되게 되는데, 재흡수 될 때 진통제가 듣지 않을 정도의 강한 급성 통증이 생기기도 한답니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9f0-1e54-11f0-8dab-f98333803df7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9ef-1e54-11f0-8dab-c5f09fcde4d6\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9f2-1e54-11f0-8dab-dba8ba4ffe64\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9f1-1e54-11f0-8dab-21ec3eb5deac\">석회성 힘줄염을 엑스레이로 촬영하면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9f4-1e54-11f0-8dab-71a7bb63a6d3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9f3-1e54-11f0-8dab-8375abfa6bb7\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-87b3a9f6-1e54-11f0-8dab-4be3fcc4a426\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87b3a9f7-1e54-11f0-8dab-6dfbb30ab7f9\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-right\" style=\"max-width:375px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-87b3a9f7-1e54-11f0-8dab-6dfbb30ab7f9\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a166864568415d48.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1455\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1506\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a166864568415d48.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a166864568415d48.jpg\" data-width=\"375\" data-height=\"387\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-87b3a9f7-1e54-11f0-8dab-6dfbb30ab7f9\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87b3a9ff-1e54-11f0-8dab-49eb6a339cc3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9f9-1e54-11f0-8dab-65549313cfab\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9f8-1e54-11f0-8dab-bdfd1efda412\">쇄골과 견봉 아래, 그리고 팔뼈(상완골)의 위쪽에 하얗게 뼈처럼 보이는 석회가 확인됩니다. (화살표 부위)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c2f9b2d7-6d1b-4a3e-8f5a-f259349edecd\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-3ccb692c-331e-4ddb-a7a8-31847aa70c0a\">&#x27;견우혈&#x27;에 침치료 등을 해서 치료 접근할 수 있는 위치입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9fb-1e54-11f0-8dab-6969688cc910\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9fa-1e54-11f0-8dab-3526ccb25711\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3a9fd-1e54-11f0-8dab-b7598c67941e\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3a9fc-1e54-11f0-8dab-8f861aff45b3\">초음파로 보면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-87b3a9ff-1e54-11f0-8dab-49eb6a339cc3\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87b3aa00-1e54-11f0-8dab-7f91f8cdc64e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-right\" style=\"max-width:375px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-87b3aa00-1e54-11f0-8dab-7f91f8cdc64e\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fa0525ef6020c0af.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1596\", \"originalHeight\" : \"893\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fa0525ef6020c0af.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fa0525ef6020c0af.jpg\" data-width=\"375\" data-height=\"209\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-87b3aa00-1e54-11f0-8dab-7f91f8cdc64e\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87b3aa01-1e54-11f0-8dab-559020063788\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-right\" style=\"max-width:375px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-87b3aa01-1e54-11f0-8dab-559020063788\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6e986d3be995a242.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1596\", \"originalHeight\" : \"851\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6e986d3be995a242.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6e986d3be995a242.jpg\" data-width=\"375\" data-height=\"199\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-87b3aa01-1e54-11f0-8dab-559020063788\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87b3d125-1e54-11f0-8dab-81e5e0006077\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3aa03-1e54-11f0-8dab-59b970ef7468\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3aa02-1e54-11f0-8dab-79acb5564503\">석회의 모양, 부위, 시기 등에 따라 조금씩 다르게 보이는데, 초음파 영상에서 석회가 생긴 걸 잘 볼 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3aa05-1e54-11f0-8dab-e52fba1f8755\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3aa04-1e54-11f0-8dab-d75d42cba4bb\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3aa07-1e54-11f0-8dab-9d3e8c6b6f96\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3aa06-1e54-11f0-8dab-3143da219f1f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3aa09-1e54-11f0-8dab-2d57d10f84e5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3aa08-1e54-11f0-8dab-cfcbd7bff643\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3aa0b-1e54-11f0-8dab-ff858582426b\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3aa0a-1e54-11f0-8dab-6779336b4622\">치료는 위에 간단히 언급했듯이 보존적치료(물리치료, 소염진통제 복용, 스테로이드 주사 요법 등)를 하거나 주사로 석회를 흡인할 수도 있고, US-PICT(Ultrasound-Guided Percutaneus Irrigation of Calcific tendinopathy) 방법이나 수술을 할 수도 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3aa0d-1e54-11f0-8dab-33a2a6ca6a91\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3aa0c-1e54-11f0-8dab-07e8a6c0d929\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3aa0f-1e54-11f0-8dab-b9168d7ba1af\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3aa0e-1e54-11f0-8dab-4182ca637a3e\">이수한의원에서는 증상의 정도(통증, 동작의 제한)와 석회의 크기(초음파 영상으로 확인), 환자의 몸 상태(허약한가, 근육질인가 등) 및 어깨관절의 활용도(직업 상 많이 써야 한다던지, 빨리 나아야 한다던지) 등을 종합 판단하여 가장 적합한 치료방법을 계획합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3aa11-1e54-11f0-8dab-df047604ad45\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3aa10-1e54-11f0-8dab-11a1f03cc16d\">물치리료, 침치료, 부항술 및 뜸, 간단한 복용약, 추나치료, 약침치료, 치료를 위한 한약 또는 몸을 보하여 회복할 힘을 보태주는 한약 등 다양한 방법을 조합하여 치료합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3d123-1e54-11f0-8dab-271a5de18132\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3d122-1e54-11f0-8dab-359bd2951194\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-87b3d125-1e54-11f0-8dab-81e5e0006077\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87b3d126-1e54-11f0-8dab-e1d7d72859c8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87b3d142-1e54-11f0-8dab-ef4385b4c4f4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3d128-1e54-11f0-8dab-594544baae54\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3d127-1e54-11f0-8dab-2df1cc348d6a\">어깨에 생기는 석회에 대해 궁금증이 풀리셨나요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3d12a-1e54-11f0-8dab-27c54b1cb173\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3d129-1e54-11f0-8dab-a9129883ca21\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3d12c-1e54-11f0-8dab-8f3afab3ee8e\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3d12b-1e54-11f0-8dab-fbb73f3e904d\">석회성 힘줄염에 대한 글은 여기서 마치겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3d12e-1e54-11f0-8dab-05ef774ff130\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3d12d-1e54-11f0-8dab-f78e4f594c48\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3d130-1e54-11f0-8dab-bfe4fe907a36\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3d12f-1e54-11f0-8dab-afe475e6f88c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3d132-1e54-11f0-8dab-fda69192ac56\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3d131-1e54-11f0-8dab-a3d34c2ab60c\">서울 동작구 사당로 218-1 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3d134-1e54-11f0-8dab-abfc866af8cb\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3d133-1e54-11f0-8dab-b58b76f2d72b\">지하철 7호선 남성역 1번출구 앞 2층</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3d136-1e54-11f0-8dab-adc394a7879d\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3d135-1e54-11f0-8dab-993f3e08bda9\">예약문의 02-584-1075</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3d138-1e54-11f0-8dab-f1e88648de80\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3d137-1e54-11f0-8dab-27cbcb5273a5\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3d13a-1e54-11f0-8dab-d9cc143ebc7a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3d139-1e54-11f0-8dab-45a925f43188\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3d13c-1e54-11f0-8dab-012ca66aea6f\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3d13b-1e54-11f0-8dab-8d4d9da268d2\">네이버 예약</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3d13e-1e54-11f0-8dab-73e5e05e3e71\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87b3d13d-1e54-11f0-8dab-29d0b51a8052\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b3d140-1e54-11f0-8dab-fb0523909d04\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic   \" id=\"SE-87b3d13f-1e54-11f0-8dab-55c2ebcb58c2\"><a href=\"https://booking.naver.com/booking/13/bizes/331349?tr&#x3D;bnm\" class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"text\" data-lin